# samblog — Project Rules

## Stack

Astro 6 (SSG) + Vue 3 (Composition API) + Tailwind CSS 4 + MDX. Node.js >= 22.12.0.

## Architecture

- `src/pages/index.astro` — root redirect: detects locale from localStorage / navigator, redirects to `/{locale}/`
- `src/pages/[locale]/` — file-based routing, all pages are locale-prefixed (en, ru, pl)
- `src/layouts/Base.astro` — HTML shell, theme script, font preloads, Umami analytics script
- `src/layouts/Post.astro` — blog post layout with sidebar TOC and share buttons
- `src/components/` — Astro components (`.astro`) and Vue interactive components (`.vue`)
- `src/components/SEO.astro` — meta tags, Open Graph, JSON-LD (Person, BlogPosting)
- `src/content/` — MDX content collections: `blog/`, `pages/`, `things/`
- `src/content.config.ts` — collection schemas (Zod)
- `src/plugins/remark-reading-time.mjs` — computes `readingTime` on blog posts (not a frontmatter field)
- `src/i18n/ui.ts` — translation strings, `src/i18n/utils.ts` — helper functions
- `src/consts.ts` — site metadata, locales, social links
- `src/styles/global.css` — design tokens, prose styles, base styles
- `public/` — static assets: images, papers (PDFs), fonts, robots.txt, _headers, CNAME, favicons

## Conventions

- Three locales: `en`, `ru`, `pl`. Default: `en`. Order in UI: EN, RU, PL.
- Dark mode is the default theme.
- All Latin text uses Cambria font (`--font-serif`). Never use `--font-sans` in components.
- No comments in code unless explaining non-obvious intent.
- Do not rename existing methods or fields.
- Do not perform major refactoring unless explicitly asked.
- Content collection `things` uses `thingId` (not `slug`) in frontmatter to avoid Astro glob loader ID conflicts.
- VK and Yandex Music links in `things` collection have `ruOnly: true` — only shown when locale is `ru`.
- Blog posts can have optional `habr` field (URL) — renders a branded Habr badge in cards and article pages.
- Scientific publication PDFs are stored in `public/papers/`.

## i18n

- UI strings go in `src/i18n/ui.ts` — all three locales must be updated together.
- Navigation keys: `nav.home`, `nav.blog`, `nav.about`, `nav.now`, `nav.things`, `nav.timer`.
- Site locale (UI language) and article locale (content language) are decoupled for blog posts.

## Analytics

Umami (privacy-friendly, no cookies). Injected in `Base.astro` only when `PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID` is set. Env var comes from `.env` locally or GitHub Actions `vars` in CI.

## Git

- Never change git config. All commits must be from `Vitaly Lyutarevich <vitaly.lyutarevich@gmail.com>`.
- Never commit or push without explicit user permission.

## Styling

- CSS custom properties defined in `global.css` under `@theme` block.
- Scoped styles in `.astro` files preferred over global CSS for component-specific styles.
- Accent color: `--color-accent` (BORK-style orange/terracotta).
